<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-10-28T18:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-10-28T18:00:00-05:00" n="293" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d293">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">891.20/174a: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Minister in Iran</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Dreyfus</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-10-28T19:00:00-04:00">October
                                    28, 1942—7 p.m.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>295. In connection with the drafting of an Agreement for a United States
                            Military Mission to Iran consisting of Colonel Schwarzkopf, Lieutenant
                            Colonel Boone and Captain Preston, the following information is urgently
                            desired: <list>
                                <label>
                                    <hi rend="italic">a</hi>.</label>
                                <item>What in your opinion should be the stated purpose of the
                                    Mission?</item>
                                <pb facs="0272" n="260" xml:id="pg_260"/>
                                <label>
                                    <hi rend="italic">b</hi>.</label>
                                <item>To what official of the Iranian Government will the Mission be
                                    responsible?</item>
                                <label>
                                    <hi rend="italic">c</hi>.</label>
                                <item>Approximate duration of the Mission?</item>
                            </list>
                        </p>
                        <p>Please discuss the above points with Colonel Schwarzkopf replying by
                            telegram and furnishing any other information which in your opinion
                            would be helpful to the Department in drafting this Agreement.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>